vote.title:
A resolution authorizing a one-year extension of the Letter of Credit Reimbursement Agreement and a Fee Agreement with JPMorgan Chase Bank, National Association from December 18, 2025 to December 17, 2026, with respect to the Love Field Airport Modernization Corporation Airport System Commercial Paper Notes, AMT Series - Not to exceed TBD $1,875,000 - Financing: Aviation Fund

*In alignment with LEAP Program.
